Comment: 1,0:00:16.91,0:00:17.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.54,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,開端便是一切都順序錯亂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,一成不變的生活地覆天翻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.50,0:00:25.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,很久很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.17,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,人還知吃吃喝喝舞中作樂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,今辛酸痛苦無止境  社會壓力超負荷
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.55,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早間新聞將這常態播放著
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,逼著我睜開雙眼  漱口洗臉
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早餐一個漢堡打發  能不能來點奇蹟使天地異變
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做什麼夢呢我傻嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.64,0:00:40.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.85,0:00:41.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.98,0:00:42.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,I wanna!!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.52,0:00:43.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing, dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Rolling, rolling
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.36,0:00:47.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Only one, my life
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.61,0:00:50.91,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,不久後人生即將畫上句號
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.91,0:00:53.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,僅有空虛又怎夠將我填飽？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.12,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.12,0:00:56.70,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.70,0:01:02.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原點  保持新鮮
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.08,0:01:05.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所願
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.05,0:01:15.18,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至盡興  玩到疲倦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.56,0:01:19.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
