Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.35,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}この日が人生のラストだと思えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:51.43,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}スティーブも失笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.52,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}なんか始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:54.77,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}Life & Death
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.86,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}もう何回目？なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:01.82,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}やめられないんだ　Like a ジャンキー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:05.11,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}もう一回　さあもう一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:10.03,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}いくぜ　この世の果てまでyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}さあ　幸せを探したいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:14.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}鍵は置いてったっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:18.33,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}生きて笑えていれば上等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:20.92,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}さあ何もない場所だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:22.96,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}何もないわけじゃないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:25.09,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}どうだい？オーライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.72,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}今日にときめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:29.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}さあ　この世の地獄で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:32.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}笑いあっていたいんだ君と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.81,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}気の向くままに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:37.40,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}さあ　全てが壊れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:39.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}そこから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:43.32,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}オーライ！今日を楽しんで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}寄り道したっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:48.03,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}急に歌い出したっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:53.41,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}全て終わる日まで
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.38,0:22:39.42,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}每一天無精打采
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.59,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}只顧著追求高效
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.59,0:22:43.55,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}雖然也不是不好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.43,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}但多少有些無聊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.35,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}如果今天就給我的人生畫上句號
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.35,0:22:51.43,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}連史蒂夫也會不禁苦笑
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.52,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}開始做點什麼吧
Comment: 1,0:22:53.52,0:22:54.77,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}Life & Death
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.86,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}已經第幾次了？然而
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.86,0:23:01.82,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}我卻無法停止  Like a 癮君子
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.82,0:23:05.11,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}再來一次 來吧再來一次
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.11,0:23:10.03,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an7\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}出發吧 直到世界盡頭yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}走吧 我想去尋找快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:14.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}把鑰匙丟在家裡也未嘗不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:18.33,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}能夠活著笑著就心滿意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:20.92,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}即便身處一片廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:22.96,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我也並非一貧如洗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:25.09,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}怎麼樣？All right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.72,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}就為今天而亢奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:29.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}來吧 我想在這個人間地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:32.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}跟你一起開懷大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:37.40,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}來吧 若是一切都不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:39.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}故事就從這裡重新展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:43.32,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}All right！盡情享受今天的精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我們可以繞繞遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:48.03,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}也可以放聲你唱我和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:53.41,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}直到世界末日到來
